<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_294" id="146v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_294_r2l1"><expan>Conrat<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü VVeinſperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l2">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> /. Als Jr vns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nam <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l4">als <add><ab facs="#facs_294_r2l3"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab></add> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> geſchehen ıſt / .
                                <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>en</expan> verſteen wir ewr gnad </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l5">vnd güten wıllen wol / vnd danken des
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel mit
                            <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l6">fleiʒʒ /. Nu ıſt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        botſchaft <expan>yecʒund<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l7"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> beÿ
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedıge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Meincʒe der ſıch gar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l8"><expan>gnediklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darvmb angenomen
                        hat / vnd <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l9">nicht gewıſſen wie <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        botſchaft <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeinen <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l10">ſcheıden wirdt / . Alſo / daʒ vvir ew cʒü
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit kein vollig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l12"><expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> künnen / vnd wenn <add><ab facs="#facs_294_r2l11">diſelb </ab></add>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>herwıd<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l14">heim kümt / wie ſie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> die
                        ſache <expan>gelaſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / . <del rend="strikethrough">So </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_294_r2l13">das </ab></add> mainen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l15">wir <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan></del> ew dann cʒü
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> /
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>embıet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / .
                        vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_line_1576567489186_280">getrawen
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol / daʒ Jr ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        darvmb <expan>anneme<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l22">vnd <expan>ernſtlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darcʒü tün
                                <add><ab facs="#facs_294_r2l21">vnd beholffen ſein </ab></add>
                        wöllet / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>v<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l23">ewr edel <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die Margarete Anno xȷ<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_294" id="146v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conrat<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü
                        Weinsperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nam <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als
                                    <add><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan></add> den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> geschehen ist,
                            <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>en</expan> versteen wir ewr gnad und güten willen
                        wol und danken des <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel mit
                                <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleizz. Nu ist
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> botschaft
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> bey
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Meincze, der sich gar
                                <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darumb angenomen hat, und
                                <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> noch nicht gewissen, wie
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> botschaft
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> seinen <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> scheiden
                        wirdt, also daz wir ew czü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit kein vollig
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> künnen. Und wenn
                            <add>diselb</add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>herwid<ex>er</ex></expan> heim kümt, wie sie
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> die sache <expan>gelasse<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        hat, <add>das</add> mainen wir ew dann czü
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> czü <expan>embiet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und
                        getrawen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol, daz ir ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        darumb <expan>anneme<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>ernstlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darczü tün <add>und beholffen
                            sein</add> wöllet. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>u<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr edel
                            <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                        Margarete anno xi<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
